## UnpublishInstruction.startAt property

Date and time when the un-publishing should be started. Should be specified in UTC format. The value will be converted to UTC time if specified with time zone shift, e.g. "2020-01-24T17:24:50+02:00" will be converted to "2020-01-24T15:24:50Z" Conversion is not happening if time zone shift is not specified.

**Signature:**

```typescript
get startAt(): Date | undefined;
```
